window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Things in the Vale of Dreams are...complicated. Anpu has tasked our intrepid heroes with recovering the next piece of the Devourer from the depths of the Forbidden Barrows, but entry to the dungeon is heavily regulated.</p> <p>With a major player guild gatekeeping most of the quests necessary to earn enough reputation to gain an audience with the elven priests promised to assist in their venture, it's going to be a hell of a time.</p> <p>Yes: stats, cursing, VR</p> <p>No: harem, explicit, wearing crocks with socks</p>"; 
